[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03092\" class=\"\">Jehoshaphat</st> <st data-num=\"07901 05973 01\">passed away</st><n id=\"1\" /> and was <st data-num=\"06912\" class=\"\">buried</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st><n id=\"2\" /> in the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">City</st> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> His <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"03088\" class=\"\">Jehoram</st><n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">replaced</st> him as <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">king</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">His <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brothers</st>, <st data-num=\"03092\" class=\"\">Jehoshaphat\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st>, were <st data-num=\"05838\" class=\"\">Azariah</st>, <st data-num=\"03171\" class=\"\">Jechiel</st>, <st data-num=\"02148\" class=\"\">Zechariah</st>, <st data-num=\"05838\" class=\"\">Azariahu</st>, <st data-num=\"04317\" class=\"\">Michael</st>, and <st data-num=\"08203\" class=\"\">Shephatiah</st>. <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> were <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> of <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"03092\" class=\"\">Jehoshaphat</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "Their <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">gave</st> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">them</st> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"04979\" class=\"\">presents</st>, including <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>, <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st>, and other <st data-num=\"04030\" class=\"\">precious items</st>, <st data-num=\"05973\">along with</st> <st data-num=\"04694\" class=\"\">fortified</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> in <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>. But he <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">gave</st> the <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st> to <st data-num=\"03088\" class=\"\">Jehoram</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> was the <st data-num=\"01060\" class=\"\">firstborn</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03088\" class=\"\">Jehoram</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">took control</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">of</st> his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st> and <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">became powerful</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> Then he <st data-num=\"02026 02719\">killed</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> his <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brothers</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">as well as</st> some of the <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03088\" class=\"\">Jehoram</st> was <st data-num=\"07970\" class=\"\">thirty</st>-<st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">two</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">old</st> when he <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">became king</st>, and he <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">reigned</st> for <st data-num=\"08083\" class=\"\">eight</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">followed</st> in the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">footsteps</st> of the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">kings</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, just <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> <st data-num=\"0256\" class=\"\">Ahab\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">dynasty</st> had <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> he <st data-num=\"01961 0802\">married</st> <st data-num=\"0256\" class=\"\">Ahab\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughter</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> He <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> in the <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">sight</st> of<n id=\"2\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "But the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> was <st data-num=\"03808 014\">unwilling</st> to <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">dynasty</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">because of</st> the <st data-num=\"01285 0834\">promise</st><n id=\"2\" /> he had <st data-num=\"03772 0834 0559\">made</st> to <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">give</st> <st data-num=\"01732 01121\">David</st> a <st data-num=\"03605 03117\">perpetual</st> <st data-num=\"05216\" class=\"\">dynasty</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">During Jehoram\u2019s<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">reign</st> <st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edom</st> <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">freed</st> themselves <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">control</st> and <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">set up</st> their <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">own</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03088\" class=\"\">Jehoram</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">crossed over</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> his <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officers</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> his <st data-num=\"07393 05973\">chariots</st>. The <st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edomites</st>, who had <st data-num=\"05437 0413\">surrounded</st> him, <st data-num=\"01961 06965\">attacked</st> at <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st> and <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">defeated</st> him and his <st data-num=\"07393\" class=\"\">chariot</st> <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officers</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edom</st> has <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">remained free</st> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">control</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> very <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> At <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">same</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> <st data-num=\"03841\" class=\"\">Libnah</st> also <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">rebelled</st> and freed themselves <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">from</st> Judah\u2019s <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">control</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> Jehoram<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">rejected</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st>. ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">He</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">also</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">built</st> <st data-num=\"01116\" class=\"\">high places</st> on the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">hills</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>; he <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">encouraged</st> the <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">residents</st> of <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st> <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">to be unfaithful</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"05080\" class=\"\">led</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> <st data-num=\"05080\" class=\"\">away</st> from the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span>.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Jehoram<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0935 0413\">received</st> this <st data-num=\"04385 0559\">letter</st> from <st data-num=\"0452\" class=\"\">Elijah</st> the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st>: \u201c<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestor</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>: \u2018You<n id=\"2\" /> have <st data-num=\"08478 0834 03808\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">followed</st> in the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">footsteps</st><n id=\"3\" /> of your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st> <st data-num=\"03092\" class=\"\">Jehoshaphat</st> <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">and</st> of<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"0609\" class=\"\">Asa</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>, ",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "but have instead <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">followed</st> in the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">footsteps</st> of the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">kings</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. You <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">encouraged</st> the people of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and the <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">residents</st> of <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st> <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">to be unfaithful</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span>, just as the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st> of <st data-num=\"0256\" class=\"\">Ahab</st> <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">does</st> in Israel.<n id=\"1\" /> You <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">also</st> <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">killed</st> your <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brothers</st>, members of your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> who were <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">better</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">than</st> you. ",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">look</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is about to <st data-num=\"04046 01419\">severely</st> <st data-num=\"05062\" class=\"\">afflict</st><n id=\"1\" /> your <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>, your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st>, your <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st>, and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> you <st data-num=\"07399\" class=\"\">own</st>. ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "And <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> will get a <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">serious</st>, <st data-num=\"02483\" class=\"\">chronic</st> <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">intestinal</st> <st data-num=\"04245\" class=\"\">disease</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">which will cause</st> your <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">intestines</st> to <st data-num=\"03318 04480 02483 03117 05921 03117\">come out</st>.\u2019\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05782\" class=\"\">stirred up</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> <st data-num=\"03088\" class=\"\">Jehoram</st> the <st data-num=\"07307 06430\">Philistines</st><n id=\"1\" /> and the <st data-num=\"06163\" class=\"\">Arabs</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> lived <st data-num=\"05921 03027\">beside</st> the <st data-num=\"03569\" class=\"\">Cushites</st>. ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">attacked</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"01234\" class=\"\">swept through</st> it.<n id=\"1\" /> They <st data-num=\"07617\" class=\"\">carried off</st> <st data-num=\"03605 07399\">everything</st> they <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">found</st> in the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">royal</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">palace</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">including</st> his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> and <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st>. <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">None</st> of his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> was <st data-num=\"07604\" class=\"\">left</st>, <st data-num=\"03588 0518\">except</st> for his <st data-num=\"06996 01121\">youngest</st>, <st data-num=\"03059\" class=\"\">Ahaziah</st>. ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">After</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st> happened, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05062\" class=\"\">afflicted</st> him with an <st data-num=\"0369 04832\">incurable</st> <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">intestinal</st> <st data-num=\"02483\" class=\"\">disease</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01961 03117 03117\">After</st> about <st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">two</st> <st data-num=\"03318 07093 03117 \">years</st> his <st data-num=\"04578\" class=\"\">intestines</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">came out</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">because of</st> the <st data-num=\"02483\" class=\"\">disease</st>, so that he <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">died</st> a <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">very painful</st> <st data-num=\"08463\" class=\"\">death</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> His <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">make</st> a <st data-num=\"08316\" class=\"\">bonfire</st> to honor him, as they had <st data-num=\"08316\" class=\"\">done</st> for his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Jehoram <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"07970\" class=\"\">thirty</st>-<st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">two</st> years <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">old</st> when he <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">became king</st> and he <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">reigned</st> <st data-num=\"08083\" class=\"\">eight</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>. <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No one</st> <st data-num=\"02532\" class=\"\">regretted</st> his <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">death</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> he was <st data-num=\"06912\" class=\"\">buried</st> in the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">City</st> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> but <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> in the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">royal</st> <st data-num=\"06913\" class=\"\">tombs</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  }
]